headline: Match Group to Announce Second Quarter 2025 Results
summary: Match Group (NASDAQ: MTCH) will release financial results for the second quarter 2025 on Tuesday, August 5, 2025 after-market close. The company will host its quarterly conference call to discuss these results at 5:00 p.m. ET on the same day.
